    <is_fda_regulated_device>No</is_fda_regulated_device>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The effect of endotracheal cuff pressure measurement technique for preventing ventilatory
      associated pneumonia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Aim of this study is to evaluate the effect of endotracheal cuff pressure measurement
      technique for preventing ventilatory associated pneumonia of severe traumatic brain injured
      patients in a tertiary level intensive care unit.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
